==Hindi==
===Etymology===
Sanskrit क्रिया
===Noun ===
'''क्रिया''' kriyā {{f}}
# Doing, performance; 
# action, act, deed; 
# undertaking
# business
# use
# work, labour; a literary work
# (in [[grammar]]) a verb
# medical treatment or practice
# a religious act or ceremony, a pious act, a duty
# obsequies
# an oath

